    "Experimentation and results MetricsTo evaluate the performance of the proposed approach, we used the following standard metrics.",
    "Precision (5.1), Recall (5.2), and F-score (5.3).",
    "The F-score is calculated as a weighted average of the Precision and Recall measurements.",
    "A clinical entity is correctly classified when the predicted label is equal to the label indicated by the annotated corpus.",
    "The performance of the medical concept extraction task is measured at the entity level."
